---
title: Sweet Thai Style Pulled Beef Tacos with Sesame Chips, Sriracha Slaw and Baby Leaf Salad
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, these tasty Sweet Thai Style Pulled Beef Tacos are perfect for a casual sharing-style dinner.
